For each batch:
  1) POSITIVE PHASE
     v (data frames)  ──► Forward GEMV (Wᵀv) ─► Sigmoid ─► p(h|v)
                         └────────────────────► OuterProd Accum (+)= v · p(h)ᵀ

  2) RECONSTRUCTION
     p(h|v)           ──► Recon GEMV (W h) ─► ṽ  (Gaussian mean, clamp)

  3) NEGATIVE PHASE
     ṽ               ──► Forward GEMV (Wᵀṽ) ─► Sigmoid ─► p(h̃|ṽ)
                         └────────────────────► OuterProd Accum (−)= ṽ · p(h̃)ᵀ

  4) UPDATE
     ΔW = AccPos − AccNeg
     W ← (1−λ)·W + μ·ΔW_prev + η·ΔW       (fixed-point, saturated)
     (Biases updated similarly)
